fa6ad1f792b139278e2870ae933d7c","tid":469833,"uid":130872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>You don't really forget someone.<br />\nYou just need to focus on other things.<br />\nFill up your schedule and you will realize no one actually lives for someone.<br />\n<br />\nPeople come and go. Some may stay. Some will leave.<br />\nThat someone just happened to be the one who left.<br />\n<br />\nGayau<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThank you so much"},{"pid":"7685efcd8ab281aebbe213c6e0ed91d79097dd6c","tid":469833,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:48:43.000Z","msg":"They won&rsquo;t forget you as well, just get your life going. You&rsquo;re not gonna pop into each other&rsquo;s life anyways"},{"pid":"762b209deee47e318f4937746a5e68ed82baddec","tid":469833,"uid":130872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>You will never forget <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nJust go on</blockquote><br />\nI hope so</blockquote><br />\nGo to gym, read books, work hard, live a better life</blockquote><br />\nI&lsquo;m a toxic j <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e274ff45b3adf9d4f50850845520b92695c50ccc","tid":469833,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:49:10.000Z","msg":"forgive yourself<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292530a64377bd62030ee8c7d5a40438b8372454","tid":469833,"uid":130872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>good memories no need to forget</blockquote><br />\nCant agree anymore"},{"pid":"61bc164550878c7f14142d70415e3c41d596a0fa","tid":